# UI and design

Before changing UI styling or adding new visual patterns, read the repo root **`DESIGN.md`** and align with existing **Tailwind** tokens (`brand.*`, `hud.*`, `semantic.*` via CSS variables where applicable). Avoid introducing one-off hex colors when a token exists.
